{"tid":1384034,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"見咁多人講大j 想吹奏一下呢位YouTuber kol 希望佢都和解到","createTime":"2019-07-29T22:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T08:29:13.000Z","uid":240566,"like":94,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b39f7a2aaca30924d7211d90ba26486b094d3c","tid":1384034,"uid":240566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:56:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係galaxyman 仲民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢由6月9號已經開始罷市 不停出黎發夢<br />\n大家都知罷市一日賺少好多錢<br />\n佢仲籌備緊開新鋪頭 壓力更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢不停係ig開po同story叫人留意呢件事<br />\n佢影響左好多90後同00後 至少我身邊唔少朋友都係比佢影響到 <br />\n<br />\n而且佢係澳門都有賣衫 有一定嘅fans 影響埋澳門年青人 令佢地更了解件事同對與錯<br />\n<br />\n最重要係佢同好多中國潮牌有合作 佢都冇理咁多 唔驚斷絕合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以認識佢 多啲幫襯佢 比佢津貼返罷市少左個啲 唔係講咩 但佢間野真係好多人上去睇 去過幾次 次次都好多人 冇開一日都賺少好多同佢啲衫褲真係一啲都唔貴 ！！！<br />\n<br />\n我知有啲連登仔話佢好串 博上位 但話矖都係真。香港人 大j都和解到 佢都得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申</span></span> 第一次開po 屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋一蚊都冇收過 只係一位由你開channel開始已經覺得你好型 好鐘意你嘅fans 我知你會睇到 希望你財源滾滾 賺多啲同勿忘初心 <br />\n<br />\n加油香港人  光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcmY6mx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcmY6mx.png&h=f4d3d13c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NruvXtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNruvXtd.png&h=81fa4308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce559ce14e4b829ed6f5ffe6f15955787d3b72d","tid":1384034,"uid":240566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:57:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a1ab6780